{"word":"G423 - ἀνεπίληπτος - anepílēptos - an-ep-eel'-ape-tos - Blameless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνεπίληπτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anepílēptos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ep-eel'-ape-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Blameless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குற்றம் சாட்டப்படாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not apprehended"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1949 - ἐπιλαμβάνομαι - epilambánomai - ep-ee-lam-ban'-om-ahee/1949\">G1949</a>; <i>not arrested</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>inculpable:</i> - blameless, unrebukeable.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1949/1949\">G1949</a>, <a href=\"#/G2638/2638\">G2638</a>, <a href=\"#/G2983/2983\">G2983</a>, <a href=\"#/G3335/3335\">G3335</a>, <a href=\"#/G3336/3336\">G3336</a>, <a href=\"#/G353/353\">G353</a>, <a href=\"#/G354/354\">G354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3880/3880\">G3880</a>, <a href=\"#/G423/423\">G423</a>, <a href=\"#/G4301/4301\">G4301</a>, <a href=\"#/G4355/4355\">G4355</a>, <a href=\"#/G4356/4356\">G4356</a>, <a href=\"#/G5274/5274\">G5274</a>"}]}